---
title: Yellow Thai Style Coconut Noodle Soup with Aubergine, Pak Choi and Peanuts
description: Our Yellow Thai Style Coconut Noodle Soup is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/yellow-thai-style-coconut-noodle-soup-826805a8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/yellow-thai-style-coconut-noodle-soup-6200d9f9ae6eb22d972f8ee8-77296008.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Asian
nutrition:
